<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ض ب<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٠٤٣ - ق ض ب]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>اقتضبَ يقتضِب، اقْتِضابًا، فهو مُقْتضِب، والمفعول مُقْتضَب<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• اقتضب الغُصْنَ:</span> قَضَبه، قطعه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• اقتضب الكلامَ:</span> ارتجله، تكلَّم به دون أن يُعِدَّه من قَبْل.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• اقتضب حديثَه:</span> أوجزه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>